---

## üöÄ Quick Start

```bash
# Install DJINN
pip install djinn-cli

# Run setup wizard (first time)
djinn setup

# Use natural language
djinn "list all docker containers"

# Or use direct commands
djinn git status
djinn docker cleanup
djinn sysinfo

# Install more plugins
djinn market install spotify
djinn spotify now
```

